name: I am dead inside.
description: Practically speaking, cells are the smallest living things. All the subcell structures -organelles- only can function inside of the cell. Otherwise, individually they are considered as a bunch of dead things. Therefore, there is one question that remains; What does this make us? A zombie or a night king?  (The sound also belongs to me, inspired from binary communications) (https://www.instagram.com/semihiyikalender/)
